title: Independent candidate Umair Khan Niazi wins NA-90 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Umair Khan Niazi has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-90 Mianwali-II by securing 1,79,820 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate Muhammad Humair Hayat Khan Niazi, who bagged 51,223 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 58.2 percent.
